data.description: 3 bedroom 1 bath one level living on a level flat yard. Nice covered front porch.   A great in town investment property.  Property is being sold AS IS Where Is.  The condition of the heat pump and appliances is unknown.  The electricity nor water is on.   This property will not qualify for FHA, VA or USDA Financing.  “This property has been placed in an upcoming online event. All bids should be submitted at www.xome.com (void where prohibited). All offers received prior to the event period should be submitted by the buyer or buyer's agent by clicking on the “Make Offer” button on the Property Details page on Xome.com. All offers will be reviewed and responded to within 3 business days. All properties are subject to a 5% buyer's premium pursuant to the Auction Participation Agreement and Terms & Conditions (minimums will apply). Please contact listing agent for details and commission paid on this property.”Seller will make no repairs.  Property is in Flood Zone A-4
